title: "Given The Movie: To the Sea" Live Performance (2024.11.10 at KT Zepp Yokohama)
overview: The official Film for the Centimillimental × Given × Syh performance concert at KT Zepp Yokohama on October 11th 2024, Available exclusively on the Bonus CD “Given the Movie: To the Sea [Limited Edition]” DVD and Blu-ray. Featuring the Live Collab performance of "Fuyu no Hanashi", "Umi e", & "Kizuato" as well as some wholesome interactions between Mafuyu's VA, Hiragi's VA, and the fans...
